Package com.authenticket.authenticket.dto.event

Class EventDtoMapper

java.lang.Object
com.authenticket.authenticket.dto.event.EventDtoMapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Function<Event,EventDisplayDto>
@Service public class EventDtoMapper extends Object implements Function<Event,EventDisplayDto>
Service class responsible for mapping Event entities to various DTOs. EventDisplayDto DTOs and performing updates on event entities.
